Common_npm_project:

public/styles/main.css
views/main.ejs
index.js

For setup a project:
npm init -y
npm i express ejs axios body-parser
package.json: add "type": "module"

setup main.ejs: html + embedded js

setup index.js: get/post/put/patch/delete to run the app

npm install express pg passport passport-local express-session bcrypt

passport authenticaltion: https://medium.com/@prashantramnyc/node-js-with-passport-authentication-simplified-76ca65ee91e5

